snippet.title: Midpoint - MathHelp.com - Geometry Help
snippet.description: For a complete lesson on midpoint, go to http://www.MathHelp.com - 1000+ online math lessons featuring a personal math teacher inside every lesson! In this lesson, students learn the segment addition postulate and the definition of a midpoint, as well as the definitions of congruent segments and segment bisectors. Students then use algebra to find missing segment lengths and answer various other questions related to midpoints, congruent segments, and segment bisectors.
